Package blf.grammar

Class BcqlBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • blf.grammar.BcqlBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BcqlListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseBlockchainListener, BaseGenerator, SemanticAnalyzer
    public class BcqlBaseListener
extends Object
implements BcqlListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of BcqlListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
